          <span style="color: white; margin: 0 5px;"> - </span>
          <a style="color: white; text-decoration: underline; margin: 0 5px;" href="https://war.ukraine.ua/donate">Donate to &#127482;&#127462;</a>
          <span style="color: white; margin: 0 5px;"> - </span>
