      <img src="/static/the-contract-mobile-landing.webp" />
    </div>

     <button id="problemJump" class="problem-jump" type="button" aria-label="Jump to why Poke exists">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M12 5V19" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <path d="M6.5 13.5L12 19L17.5 13.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </button>
 
    <section class="poke-problem-section" id="why-poke">

      <!-- Hero statement -->
      <div class="ppb-hero">
         <h1 class="ppb-hero-title">THE WEB<br>GOT WEIRD.</h1>
        <p class="ppb-hero-sub">
          ads on every surface. tracking on every click. dark patterns right where the buttons should be.
          the internet stopped feeling like yours... Poke is the calmer place.
        </p>
        <div class="ppb-hero-actions">
          <a class="ppb-btn" href="/search">Start Discovering!</a>
          <a class="ppb-btn" href="/privacy">Read the privacy policy</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Narrative + Reasons two-column -->
      <div class="ppb-two">
        <div class="ppb-narrative">
           <h2>a softer corner of the internet.</h2>
          <p>
            no weird little traps, no lecture wall when u just wanna watch something.
            poke strips it all back so u can actually use the web! without the web using you back :3
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="ppb-reasons-list">
          <div class="ppb-reason">
            <div class="ppb-reason-n">01</div>
            <div class="ppb-reason-body">
              <strong>Tracking everywhere</strong>
              <span>your watch habits and clicks shouldn't be somebody else's product.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ppb-reason">
            <div class="ppb-reason-n">02</div>
            <div class="ppb-reason-body">
              <strong>Pages drowning in noise</strong>
              <span>ads & clutter... all fighting for ur attention around the actual content.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ppb-reason">
            <div class="ppb-reason-n">03</div>
            <div class="ppb-reason-body">
              <strong>Lock-in and control</strong>
              <span>giant platforms shouldn't get to decide how the whole web feels to use.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ppb-reason">
            <div class="ppb-reason-n">04</div>
            <div class="ppb-reason-body">
              <strong>Real-world harm</strong>
              <span>tech shouldn't scale propaganda, mass surveillance, or worse.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

   
      <!-- Answer strip -->
      <div class="ppb-answer">
        <strong>Poke exists for ppl who are tired of all that.</strong>
        a privacy app that's calmer, lighter, and just nicer to use :3
      </div>

